# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  AUTH – Session Lifecycle (cookie-based)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [Positive][Session] Login before validate/refresh/logout chain
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{MatrixEmailWithPhone}}",
  "password": "{{TestPassword}}"
}

###

### [Positive][Session] Validate authenticated session (requires login cookie)
GET {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/validate

###

### [Positive][Session] Refresh authenticated session (requires refresh cookie)
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh

###

### [Manual][Session] Refresh rate limiting (expect 429 after >20 refresh calls per minute from same client)
# Re-run the refresh request rapidly (for example with a loop in terminal) to verify AuthRefreshAttempts policy.
# Example PowerShell:
# 1..25 | % { iwr -Method Post -UseBasicParsing "{{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh" }

###

### [Manual][Login] Login rate limiting (expect 429 after >10 login calls per minute from same client)
# Example PowerShell:
# 1..12 | % {
#   $body = @{ email = "{{MatrixEmailWithPhone}}"; password = "{{TestWrongPassword}}" } | ConvertTo-Json
#   iwr -Method Post -UseBasicParsing -ContentType "application/json" -Body $body "{{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login"
# }

###

### [Manual][Login] Lockout after repeated bad password attempts (expect 429, then valid login works after lockout window)
# Trigger lockout with 5 consecutive wrong-password attempts against the same mechanic account.
# Then verify:
# 1) immediate valid-password login returns 429 during lockout window,
# 2) valid-password login succeeds after lockout expires.

###

### [Positive][Session] Logout current session
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout

###

### [Negative][Session] Validate after logout (401 expected)
GET {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/validate

###

### [Negative][Session] Refresh without active cookie session (401 expected)
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh

###

### [Negative][Session] Logout without active access cookie (401 expected)
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  HEALTH – Aspire default endpoints (Development only)
#  Mapped by MapDefaultEndpoints() in ServiceDefaults.
#  No authentication required; only available when ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT = Development.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [Positive][Health] Full health check — all registered checks must pass (200 Healthy expected)
GET {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/health

###

### [Positive][Health] Liveness check — only "live"-tagged checks (200 Healthy expected)
GET {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/alive

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
